---
import "../styles/global.css";
---
<main class="flex flex-col gap-36 items-start px-5 py-0 mx-auto my-0 w-full max-w-screen-xl max-md:gap-20 max-md:px-4 max-md:py-0 max-sm:gap-16 max-sm:px-2.5 max-sm:py-0">
  <section class="flex gap-24 items-center w-full max-md:flex-col max-md:gap-10 max-md:items-center">
    <header class="flex flex-col gap-6 items-start w-[509px] max-md:items-center max-md:w-full max-md:text-center max-md:max-w-[600px]">
      <h1 class="w-full text-6xl font-bold text-black max-md:w-full max-md:text-5xl max-sm:text-4xl">
        Confianza y bienestar en tu hogar
      </h1>
      <p class="text-2xl text-justify text-black h-[168px] w-[468px] max-md:w-full max-md:text-xl max-md:text-center max-sm:text-lg">
        Somos especialistas en la selección y gestión integral de personal doméstico, comprometidos con ofrecer soluciones confiables, profesionales y humanas.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-6 justify-center items-center w-full max-md:flex-col max-md:gap-4 max-md:w-full">
        <button class="gap-2.5 p-5 text-2xl text-white bg-sky-900 rounded-xl cursor-pointer w-[250px] max-md:w-full max-md:max-w-[300px] max-sm:p-4 max-sm:text-xl">
          Servicios
        </button>
        <button class="gap-2.5 p-5 text-2xl text-white bg-sky-900 rounded-xl cursor-pointer w-[250px] max-md:w-full max-md:max-w-[300px] max-sm:p-4 max-sm:text-xl">
          Contactanos
        </button>
      </div>
    </header>
    <img
      src="https://cdn.builder.io/api/v1/image/assets/TEMP/5b33d70270f732475345cc390ba08556499df7f0?placeholderIfAbsent=true"
      alt="Banner ilustrativo de servicios domésticos"
      class="rounded-xl h-[516px] w-[676px] max-md:w-full max-md:h-auto max-md:rounded-xl max-md:max-w-[600px]"
    />
  </section>

  <section class="flex gap-16 items-center w-full max-md:flex-col max-md:gap-8 max-md:w-full">
    <article class="flex gap-2.5 justify-center items-center px-8 py-11 bg-white rounded-xl border-2 border-solid shadow-sm border-slate-700 h-[436px] w-[310px] max-md:px-5 max-md:py-8 max-md:w-full max-md:h-auto max-md:max-w-[400px] max-sm:px-4 max-sm:py-6">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 justify-center items-center w-full">
        <div class="relative h-[120px] w-[120px] max-sm:h-[100px] max-sm:w-[100px]">
          <img
            src="https://cdn.builder.io/api/v1/image/assets/TEMP/743cf72d321fcd3ef93a88987f0b2776aa69b9b1?placeholderIfAbsent=true"
            alt="Ícono de capacitación"
            class="absolute top-0 left-0 h-[118px] w-[118px] z-[2] max-sm:h-[98px] max-sm:w-[98px]"
          />
          <div class="absolute top-0.5 left-0.5 rounded-3xl bg-slate-700 bg-opacity-50 h-[93px] rotate-[18.945deg] w-[93px] max-sm:h-[78px] max-sm:w-[78px]"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 items-start w-full">
          <h2 class="w-full text-2xl font-bold text-black max-sm:text-xl">
            Capacitación
          </h2>
          <p class="w-full text-xl text-justify text-black max-sm:text-lg">
            A través de alianzas con Presto y otros aliados especializados, ofrecemos formación en áreas clave
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="flex gap-2.5 justify-center items-center px-8 py-11 bg-white rounded-xl border-2 border-solid shadow-sm border-slate-700 h-[436px] w-[310px] max-md:px-5 max-md:py-8 max-md:w-full max-md:h-auto max-md:max-w-[400px] max-sm:px-4 max-sm:py-6">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 justify-center items-center w-full">
        <div class="relative h-[120px] w-[120px] max-sm:h-[100px] max-sm:w-[100px]">
          <img
            src="https://cdn.builder.io/api/v1/image/assets/TEMP/970ee83c5e4011aae6de321cf2576e28199c0b97?placeholderIfAbsent=true"
            alt="Ícono de selección"
            class="absolute top-0 left-0 h-[118px] w-[118px] z-[2] max-sm:h-[98px] max-sm:w-[98px]"
          />
          <div class="absolute left-0 top-1 rounded-3xl bg-slate-700 bg-opacity-50 h-[93px] rotate-[-15deg] w-[93px] max-sm:h-[78px] max-sm:w-[78px]"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 items-start w-full">
          <h2 class="w-full text-2xl font-bold text-black max-sm:text-xl">
            Selección
          </h2>
          <p class="w-full text-xl text-justify text-black max-sm:text-lg">
            Cada candidato pasa por filtros psicológicos, entrevistas por competencias.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="flex gap-2.5 justify-center items-center px-8 py-11 bg-white rounded-xl border-2 border-solid shadow-sm border-slate-700 h-[436px] w-[310px] max-md:px-5 max-md:py-8 max-md:w-full max-md:h-auto max-md:max-w-[400px] max-sm:px-4 max-sm:py-6">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 justify-center items-center w-full">
        <div class="relative h-[120px] w-[120px] max-sm:h-[100px] max-sm:w-[100px]">
          <img
            src="https://cdn.builder.io/api/v1/image/assets/TEMP/4ceeea1c54b98122f5671a2e93fc5d12c2ebcb37?placeholderIfAbsent=true"
            alt="Ícono de evaluación"
            class="absolute top-0 left-0 h-[118px] w-[118px] z-[2] max-sm:h-[98px] max-sm:w-[98px]"
          />
          <div class="absolute left-0 top-0.5 rounded-3xl bg-slate-700 bg-opacity-50 h-[93px] rotate-[70.931deg] w-[93px] max-sm:h-[78px] max-sm:w-[78px]"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 items-start w-full">
          <h2 class="w-full text-2xl font-bold text-black max-sm:text-xl">
            Evaluación
          </h2>
          <p class="w-full text-xl text-justify text-black max-sm:text-lg">
            Aplicamos un sistema de evaluación de última generación, desarrollado en Israel.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </section>
</main>